'''''Idahosa Trails''''' ni film yikinamico yo muri [[Nigeriya]] 2017 yanditswe, yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Stanlee Ohikhuare<ref>https://filmfreeway.com/IdahosaTrails</ref> . Irimo Charles Okafor, David Schifter, Liz Benson, Osas Ighodaro, Frank Donga <ref>https://medium.com/@thrivemediadistrib2/idahosa-trails-press-release-the-indiefest-awards-usa-c234d55203fc</ref>. Ishingiye ku bunararibonye bw’umunyamakuru w’umunyamerika witwa Thomas Book (ugaragazwa na David Schifter) ushaka kubaza arikiyesipoki  Benson Idahosa(ugaragazwa na Charles Okafor) ashingiye ku myumvire ye ku ruhare Idahosa yagize mu gukira mu buryo bw'igitangaza umuyobozi w'icyamamare muri Umujyi wa Benin<ref>https://nollywoodobserver.wordpress.com/tag/stanlee-ohikhuare/</ref>, gukira kwe kwabayeho nyuma yimyaka itandatu muri koma. Iyi filime yasohotse mu mpera z'Ukwakira 2017 na Mighty Jot Studios mu mujyi wa Benin, muri [[Nijeriya]]<ref>https://connectnigeria.com/articles/idahosa-trails-movie-cinemas/</ref> . 

== Umugambi ==
Igitabo cya Thomas kiri mu rugendo rugana mu mujyi wa kera wa Bénin, muri [[Nijeriya]]<ref>https://worshippersgh.com/idahosa-new-christian-movie-honor-late-archbishop-benson-idahosa/</ref>, kugira ngo ukore documentaire y’iperereza ku mihango y'ibanga yakozwe mu gihe cyo kwimika Oba nshya<ref>https://www.informationng.com/2017/11/idahosa-trails-premieres-amidst-applause.html</ref>. Ntiyashoboye kubona amakuru ahagije kubera urwego rwo hejuru rwibanga ruzengurutse imihango.<ref>https://tribuneonlineng.com/charles-okafor-plays-late-benson-idahosa-in-idahosa-trails/</ref> Mugihe yitegura kuva mu mujyi, yumva inkuru yumukuru wamamaye waho wari umaze kubyuka muri koma yimyaka itandatu ahitamo kwandika inkuru.<ref>https://nlist.ng/people/stanlee-ohikhuare-177/credits/</ref> Yizeye ko inkuru izaba indishyi zimwe na zimwe kubera ko atabonye amakuru ku cyicaro gikuru, yahisemo kujya mu bitaro. Mu bitaro, umuforomo atanga ubufasha bwo gusobanura igihe abaza umugabo<ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2017/10/coming-soon-idahosa-trails.html</ref>. Arashoboye kubaza ikibazo kimwe mbere yuko abagize umuryango wumugabo binjira kugirango bahagarike ikiganiro cye. Mu kiganiro kigufi, Thomas yashoboye kubona izina ryumugabo, izina Idahosa . Ageze mucyumba cye cya hoteri yumva izina rimwe kuri TV  ya Idahosa World Outreach<ref>https://thenativemag.com/see-full-list-nominees-6th-edition-africa-magic-viewers-choice-awards/</ref>. Yibwira ko Idahosa igomba kuba yaragize uruhare runini mu gukira k'umusaza. Yandika aderesi na nimero ya terefone yerekanwe, maze yerekeza ku cyicaro gikuru cya Idahosa World Outreach mu mujyi wa Benin. Ageze mu rusengero, Thomas ahura n’umupasitori ukiri muto uzwi ku izina rya Pasiteri Osas (Kunle Idowu) amusaba kugaruka bukeye kugira ngo abonane na Benson Idahosa<ref>https://businessday.ng/life-arts/article/movie-trailer-idahosa-trails/</ref>. Pasiteri ukiri muto aha Thomas igitabo cyo gusoma kuri Idahosa. Kubera umunezero witerambere rishya, Thomas yongeye guhindura indege atangira kwitegura iyi nkuru nshya ya Idahosa. Ageze mu cyumba cye cya hoteri, Thomas yahinduye igitabo n'amaso asinziriye<ref>https://www.informationng.com/2017/11/idahosa-trails-premieres-amidst-applause.html</ref>, maze agwa mu kantu maze yisanga mu kongera gushyira mu bikorwa inkuru ivugwa muri iki gitabo. Bukeye, Thomas ahura na Pasiteri Osas maze bahagarara ahantu henshi batatsinzwe ahantu hatandukanye aho pasiteri ukiri muto yasezeranije Thomas ko bazabona Idahosa bakabona inkuru ye<ref>https://worshippersgh.com/idahosa-new-christian-movie-honor-late-archbishop-benson-idahosa/</ref>. Iminsi ibiri irashize kandi Thomas ntashobora guhura na Idahosa ariko buri joro agarutse mucyumba cye cya hoteri, akomeza gusoma igitabo kuri Idahosa<ref>https://selahafrik.com/2017/10/idahosa-trails-trailer/</ref>. Kimwe nijoro rya mbere, arasinzira asoma igitabo maze yibonera kongera gushyirwaho inkuru zerekanwa muri iki gitabo. Yakomeje gukurikira Pasiteri Osas agamije kujya kubaza Arkiyepiskopi Idahosa<ref>http://theoloja.blogspot.com/2017/08/idahosa-trails-review-by-ngozi-mcewen.html</ref>. Umunsi umwe mbere yuko Thomas ateganijwe kugenda, yatunguwe no kumenya ko Idahosa yapfuye. Ubu buvumbuzi buganisha ku guterana amagambo hagati ye na Pasiteri Osas biganisha ku maso. Mugihe ibintu bitunguranye, Thomas Yatewe nimpanuka isiga Pasiteri aryamye hasi nta bwenge<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Frank_Donga</ref>. Yari afite amatsiko yo kumva uruhare rwa Idahosa mu gitangaza kigaragara cy'umusaza yabajije mu bitaro. Pasiteri Osas yatekereje ko Thomas azi urupfu rwa Idahosa maze akeka ko yashakaga gusa kubaza abantu ubuzima bwabo umurimo wa Idahosa wagize ingaruka nziza<ref>https://tribuneonlineng.com/charles-okafor-plays-late-benson-idahosa-in-idahosa-trails/</ref>. Thomas, ubu urujijo agomba guhuriza hamwe ibimenyetso kuko abonye imbaraga zo gutangira urugendo rwo kuvumbura; kubona ukuri, kwizera n'agakiza<ref>https://filmfreeway.com/IdahosaTrails</ref>.

